query:
SELECT cp.id, cp.url, cp.displayOrder, cp.isMain 
FROM container_photos cp
JOIN containers c ON cp.containerId = c.id
WHERE c.externalId = 'QWEU2600945'
ORDER BY cp.displayOrder;
